data.description: Wonderful POOL HOME in a GREAT LOCATION! 2021 ROOF! You will notice the diligent care this home has received starting with the mature lanscaping and GREAT CURB APPEAL! FULLY FENCED YARD! When you enter you are greeted with beautiful LUXURY VINYL FLOORING throughout and a cozy living room and Dining room area. You will LOVE your ultra LOW ELECTRIC BILL due to your whole House SOLAR PANELS! Loaded with updates that include NEW ELECTRIC PANEL , PLUMBING RE-PIPED, the well pump and pool pump were replaced in 2021. 2016 A/C. Generator electric transfer switch installed in 2022. BRAND NEW HURRICANE RATED FRONT DOOR, IMPACT WINDOWS and SLIDING GLASS DOORS.  Any cook will enjoy the completely remodeled kitchen with stainless steel appliances. LOOK AT THAT AWESOME REFRIGERATOR! More than ample cabinet and counter space as well as extra built in cabinetry affords all the room you need for cooking and entertaining.  Your guests will LOVE the updated pool bath with fine cabinetry and pleasing decor. Like the rest of the home, the owner's suite is updated and spacious. The HUGE OVERSIZE SREENED AND TILED LANAI will be great for entertaining and BBQ pool parties.  ACT NOW!
